微软研究院博客 - 微软研究院 https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/ 2024 年 6 月 17 日星期一 15:54:04 +0000 en-US每小时1 https://wordpress.org/?v=6.5.3
 AutoGen Studio 简介：用于构建多代理工作流程的低代码界面https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/introducing-autogen-studio-a-low-code-interface-for-building-multi-agent-workflows/Brenda Potts Mon, 17 Jun 2024 16:00:00 +0000Research Blog https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/?p=1045743 <p> AutoGen Studio 基于 Microsoft 灵活的开源 AutoGen 框架构建，用于编排 AI 代理，提供直观的用户友好界面，使开发人员能够快速构建、测试、定制和共享多代理 AI 解决方案，而无需编写代码。</p><p> <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/introducing-autogen-studio-a-low-code-interface-for-building-multi-agent-workflows/">AutoGen Studio 简介：用于构建多代理工作流程的低代码界面一</a>文首先出现在<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research">Microsoft Research</a>上。</p> ; 
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1.jpg" alt="白色图标代表（从左到右）代理（多个）、工作流程、任务和在蓝色到紫色到粉色渐变背景上的编码。" class="wp-image-1047747" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1.jpg 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-1066x600.jpg 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-655x368.jpg 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-240x135.jpg 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-640x360.jpg 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-960x540.jpg 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_AutoGen-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></figure><p>人工智能应用的多代理方法，即多个基于模型的代理协作解决问题，正在成为完成日益复杂的任务的强大范例。 2023 年 9 月，我们发布了<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/project/autogen/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">AutoGen——</a>一个基于 Python 的灵活开源框架，用于定义、配置和组合 AI 代理来驱动多代理应用程序。今天，我们推出 AutoGen Studio（版本 0.1.0）——一个用于快速构建、测试和共享多代理解决方案的低代码界面。 AutoGen Studio 基于 AutoGen 构建，继承了其特性和功能，同时提供用户友好且直观的界面来创建和自定义代理，几乎不需要任何编码。 </p><div class="annotations " data-bi-aN="margin-callout"><ul class="annotations__list card depth-16 bg-body p-4 annotations__list--left"><li class="annotations__list-item"> <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/project/autogen/" target="_self" class="annotations__link font-weight-semibold text-decoration-none" data-bi-type="annotated-link" aria-label="AutoGen" data-bi-aN="margin-callout" data-bi-cN="AutoGen">自动生成</a> <span class="annotations__type d-block text-uppercase font-weight-semibold text-neutral-300 small">项目</span><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/project/autogen/" target="_self" class="annotations__link font-weight-semibold text-decoration-none" data-bi-type="annotated-link" aria-label="AutoGen" data-bi-aN="margin-callout" data-bi-cN="AutoGen"><span class="glyph-append glyph-append-chevron-right glyph-append-xsmall"></span></a></li></ul></div><p>自发布以来的九个月内， <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/project/autogen/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">AutoGen <span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开）</span></a>已被研究人员、开发人员和爱好者广泛采用，他们创建了各种新颖且<a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://youtu.be/j_mtwQiaLGU?si=zQsAyk-xUeElSQcv" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">令人兴奋的应用程序<span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开）</span></a> - 从市场研究到互动教育医疗领域数据分析管道的工具。 AutoGen 在 GitHub 上拥有超过 290 名社区贡献者，Python 包的下载量达到 890,000 次（截至 2024 年 5 月），AutoGen 仍然是构建和研究多代理 AI 应用程序的领先框架。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1.png" alt="AutoGen Studio 用户界面：PDF Book Gen 会话" class="wp-image-1045800" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1.png 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1-300x169.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1-768x432.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1-1066x600.png 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1-655x368.png 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1-240x135.png 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1-640x360.png 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1-960x540.png 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_pdf-book_fig1-1280x720.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> AutoGen Studio 界面的屏幕截图显示了使用两个代理来解决任务“创建一本 4 页儿童 .pdf 书籍，其中包含有关西雅图天气模式的详细信息和图片”时的结果。</figcaption></figure><p> AutoGen Studio 是帮助开发人员推进多代理范例的下一步。我们希望以负责任的方式为想要构建多代理应用程序来解决现实世界问题的不同受众（从学术研究人员到跨行业的专业开发人员）提供多代理解决方案。想象一下，可以使用代理来自动化您的假期计划和杂货购物、管理您的个人财务、帮助您实现学习目标或执行您关心的任何其他任务。您将如何构建这样的代理？你会给他们什么能力？你将如何让他们一起工作？您如何确保它们按预期工作？ </p><div class="annotations " data-bi-aN="margin-callout"><ul class="annotations__list card depth-16 bg-body p-4 annotations__list--right"><li class="annotations__list-item"> <span class="annotations__type d-block text-uppercase font-weight-semibold text-neutral-300 small">下载</span><a href="https://github.com/microsoft/autogen/tree/main/samples/apps/autogen-studio" target="_blank" class="annotations__link font-weight-semibold text-decoration-none" data-bi-type="annotated-link" aria-label="AutoGen Studio" data-bi-aN="margin-callout" data-bi-cN="AutoGen Studio">AutoGen Studio<span class="glyph-append glyph-append-share glyph-append-xsmall"></span></a></li></ul></div><p>这些问题促使我们建立 AutoGen Studio。借助 AutoGen Studio，开发人员可以快速构建、测试、部署代理和代理团队（工作流程）并与社区共享。</p><p><strong>注意</strong>：AutoGen 主要是一个开发工具，用于实现快速原型设计和研究。它不是一个生产就绪的工具。请参阅<a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://github.com/microsoft/autogen/tree/main/samples/apps/autogen-studio" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">GitHub 存储库<span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开）</span></a>和<a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://microsoft.github.io/autogen/docs/autogen-studio/getting-started/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">文档<span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开），</span></a>了解如何开始的说明。</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-can-you-do-with-autogen-studio-right-now">您现在可以使用 AutoGen Studio 做什么？</h2><p>我们构建 AutoGen Studio 时牢记以下目标：</p><ul><li>降低构建多代理应用程序的进入门槛</li><li>促进多代理解决方案的快速原型设计和测试</li><li>通过允许用户共享和重复使用该技术来培养专​​业知识和社区</li></ul><p>借助 AutoGen Studio 的早期版本（v 0.1.0），用户可以通过用户界面快速创作代理工作流程、交互式测试和调试代理、重用工件以及部署工作流程。 </p><figure class="wp-block-embed aligncenter is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe title="AutoGen Studio 演示" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/wz8cAgHhcpU?feature=oembed&rel=0" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">上面的视频展示了用户如何创建技能和模型、将它们附加到代理、创建代理工作流程、在 AutoGen Studio 中测试和部署它们。只需点击几下即可完成所有操作。</figcaption></figure><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="rapidly-author-agent-workflows">快速创作代理工作流程</h3><p>AutoGen Studio 提供了一个“构建”部分，用户可以从预定义代理库中进行选择，并将它们组成可以在几分钟内完成任务的团队（工作流程）。此外，用户可以通过图形用户界面使用基础模型、提示、技能（完成特定任务的 Python 函数，例如从天气提供者获取天气）和工作流程来定制代理和代理团队。工作流可以是顺序的（其中代理按预定义的顺序执行操作）或自主聊天（其中代理执行的顺序可能由大型语言模型、自定义逻辑驱动，所有这些都基于任务的状态）。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2.png" alt="AutoGen Studio 用户界面：代理配置" class="wp-image-1045803" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2.png 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2-300x169.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2-768x432.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2-1066x600.png 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2-655x368.png 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2-240x135.png 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2-640x360.png 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2-960x540.png 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_author_fig2-1280x720.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">在 AutoGen Studio 中，可以通过用户界面配置代理。模型和技能可以与代理相关联，代理可以组成自主聊天和顺序工作流程。</figcaption></figure><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="debug-and-test-agents">调试和测试代理</h3><p>AutoGen Studio 允许开发人员立即测试各种任务的工作流程并查看生成的工件（例如图像、代码和文档）。开发人员还可以在处理任务时查看代理工作流程的“内心独白”，并查看分析信息，例如与运行相关的成本（例如轮数和令牌数量）以及代理操作（例如是否调用了工具）以及代码执行的结果）。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a.png" alt="AutoGen Studio 用户界面：配置文件示例工作流程" class="wp-image-1045806" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a.png 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a-300x169.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a-768x432.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a-1066x600.png 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a-655x368.png 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a-240x135.png 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a-640x360.png 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a-960x540.png 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_test_fig3a-1280x720.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></figure><figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b.png" alt="AutoGen Studio 用户界面：示例工作流程" class="wp-image-1045809" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b.png 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b-300x169.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b-768x432.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b-1066x600.png 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b-655x368.png 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b-240x135.png 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b-640x360.png 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b-960x540.png 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_profile_fig3b-1280x720.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">在 AutoGen Studio 中，用户可以测试工作流程、查看结果以及查看分析代理操作的可视化效果（例如使用工具或执行代码的频率）。</figcaption></figure><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="artifact-reuse-and-deployment">工件重用和部署</h3><p>用户可以下载他们创建的技能、代理和工作流配置，并共享和重用这些工件。 AutoGen Studio 还提供了一个无缝流程来导出工作流并将其部署为应用程序编程接口 (API)，这些应用程序可以在将工作流部署为 API 的其他应用程序中使用。</p><p>具体来说，工作流可以导出为 JavaScript 对象表示法 (JSON) 文件并加载到任何 Python 应用程序中，从命令行作为 API 端点启动或包装到可部署在 Azure 容器应用程序或 Azure Web 应用程序等云服务上的 Dockerfile 中。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4.png" alt="AutoGen Studio 用户界面：导出工作流程" class="wp-image-1045812" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4.png 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4-300x169.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4-768x432.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4-1066x600.png 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4-655x368.png 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4-240x135.png 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4-640x360.png 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4-960x540.png 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_export_fig4-1280x720.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">在 AutoGen Studio 中，用户可以将代理工作流导出为 JSON 配置文件，然后在任何 Python 应用程序中重用它们，从命令行将其作为 API 启动或部署在 Azure 容器应用程序和 Azure Web 应用程序等云服务上。 </figcaption></figure><div class="border-bottom border-top border-gray-300 mt-5 mb-5 msr-promo text-center text-md-left alignwide" data-bi-aN="promo" data-bi-id="956142"><p class="msr-promo__label text-gray-800 text-center text-uppercase"><span class="px-4 bg-white display-inline-block font-weight-semibold small">微软研究院播客</span></p><div class="row pt-3 pb-4 align-items-center"><div class="msr-promo__media col-12 col-md-5"> <a class="bg-gray-300" href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/podcast/collaborators-holoportation-communication-technology-with-spencer-fowers-and-kwame-darko/" aria-label="Collaborators: Holoportation&#x2122; communication technology with Spencer Fowers and Kwame Darko" data-bi-cN="Collaborators: Holoportation&#x2122; communication technology with Spencer Fowers and Kwame Darko" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" class="w-100 display-block" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prod/2023/06/collaborators_3DTelemed_1400x788.jpg" /></a></div><div class="msr-promo__content p-3 px-5 col-12 col-md"><h2 class="h4">合作者：全息传输<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Spencer Fowers 和 Kwame Darko 的通信技术</h2><p class="large">Spencer Fowers 和 Kwame Darko 详细介绍了 Holoportation 背后的技术以及围绕该技术构建的电信设备如何将患者和医生聚集在一起（当患者和医生待在同一个房间并不容易的情况下），并讨论了这项工作的潜在影响。 </p><div class="wp-block-buttons justify-content-center justify-content-md-start"><div class="wp-block-button"> <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/podcast/collaborators-holoportation-communication-technology-with-spencer-fowers-and-kwame-darko/" class="btn btn-brand glyph-append glyph-append-chevron-right" aria-label="Listen now" data-bi-cN="Collaborators: Holoportation&#x2122; communication technology with Spencer Fowers and Kwame Darko" target="_blank">现在听</a></div></div></div><!--/.msr-promo__content--></div><!--/.msr-promo__inner-wrap--><span id="label-external-link" class="sr-only" aria-hidden="true">在新选项卡中打开</span></div><!--/.msr-promo--><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-the-community-creating-with-autogen-studio">社区正在使用 AutoGen Studio 创建什么？</h2><p>在过去的几个月里，我们分享了 AutoGen Studio 的早期版本，该版本在 pypi 上的下载量已超过 154,000 次（2024 年 1 月至 5 月）。我们对早期使用模式的观察（基于 GitHub <a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://github.com/microsoft/autogen/discussions?discussions_q=is%3Aopen+autogen+studio" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">讨论<span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开）</span></a> 、 <a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://discord.com/channels/1153072414184452236/1192280262558625842" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Discord <span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开）</span></a>和<a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=autogen+studio" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Youtube <span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开</span></a><a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://github.com/microsoft/autogen/discussions?discussions_q=is%3Aopen+autogen+studio" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><span class="sr-only">）</span></a>等社交平台的反馈）表明 AutoGen Studio推动一批具有基本技术能力（即可以安装该工具）并且有兴趣快速测试想法但编程技能有限的新用户群体。</p><p>我们已经看到这些用户原型示例涵盖旅行计划、pdf 手册生成、市场研究、结构化数据提取、视频生成和可视化生成等任务。重要的是，这些任务只需定义代理、让它们访问大型语言模型和技能、将代理添加到工作流以及使用这些工作流运行任务即可完成。 </p><figure class="wp-block-embed aligncenter is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy" title="AutoGen 工作室 - BookGen" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/VT5ap_ec1jo?feature=oembed&rel=0" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">用户正在探索早期的用例，例如报告/书籍生成，如上面的屏幕截图所示。在这里，定义了两个代理并授予其访问生成图像的技能的权限。然后，代理被组成一个工作流程，在该工作流程中交换消息和操作以解决生成 pdf 报告的任务。</figcaption></figure><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="open-research-questions-and-next-steps">开放的研究问题和后续步骤</h2><p>协调能够探索计划、反思行动和协作的代理团队，为构建解决挑战性任务的工具提供了机会。我们相信，我们只是触及了多智能体范式可能实现的表面，关于如何最好地利用基础模型还有很多未知，更不用说基于基础模型的智能体和多智能体解决方案了。</p><p>这为进一步研究留下了许多机会。</p><p>例如，多代理范式中代理之间复杂的相互作用，特别是对于日益复杂和动态的领域，凸显了多代理评估和工具的许多机会。开放性问题包括：</p><ul><li>我们如何衡量跨任务代理的性能、可靠性和可重用性？</li><li>我们如何才能更好地了解代理商的优势和局限性？</li><li>我们如何探索替代方案和结果？</li><li>我们如何比较不同的代理架构和协作协议？</li></ul><p>这些问题需要新的方法和指标来捕获多代理范式的多方面，并为开发人员和用户提供可操作的见解。</p><p>随着我们对多代理范式的理解逐渐成熟，另一个机会是提炼设计模式和最佳实践，为不同类型的任务构建有效的代理团队。例如：</p><ul><li>针对给定问题，最佳代理数量和组成是多少？</li><li>在代理之间分配责任和协调行动的最佳方式是什么？</li><li>集中式和分散式控制之间，或者同质和异构代理之间的权衡是什么？</li><li>我们如何利用人工监督和反馈来提高代理的可靠性和安全性？</li></ul><p>这些问题需要系统研究和实证评估，以发现设计多智能体解决方案的关键维度和原则。</p><p>最后，随着代理在我们的数字世界中变得更加长寿和普遍，一个公开的挑战是自动化和优化代理创建过程本身。例如：</p><ul><li>我们如何根据任务要求和可用资源动态生成代理？</li><li>我们如何调整代理参数工作流程配置以获得最佳性能？</li><li>我们如何使代理团队适应不断变化的环境和用户偏好？</li></ul><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="future-design-improvements">未来的设计改进</h2><p>当然，我们将 AutoGen Studio 视为研究许多此类研究问题的潜在工具 - 从创作工作流程的用户体验改进到可共享工件库，再到用于理解代理行为的高级工具。</p><p>我们目前正在 AutoGen Studio 中开发新的拖放体验，旨在改变用户创作多代理工作流程的方式。我们的新视觉画布允许用户轻松编排和连接代理，为定义协作动态提供直观的界面。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5.png" alt="AutoGen Studio 用户界面：可视化工作流程设计" class="wp-image-1045815" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5.png 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5-300x169.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5-768x432.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5-1066x600.png 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5-655x368.png 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5-240x135.png 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5-640x360.png 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5-960x540.png 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_drag-skill_fig5-1280x720.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> AutoGen 的新可视化画布界面允许用户轻松编排和连接代理，为定义协作动态提供直观的界面。技能和模型等实体可以通过拖放交互与代理相关联。</figcaption></figure><p><strong>可视化工作流程设计：</strong>我们增强的用户界面的核心是可视化画布，您可以在其中真实地看到您的工作流程变得栩栩如生。将不同的代理拖放到画布上以构建复杂的对话模式。这种图形方法不仅简化了初始设置，而且使修改代理和工作流程的过程更加直观。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="3238" height="1850" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_skillview.png" alt="AutoGen 的新可视化画布界面允许用户在同一视图窗格中可视化代理交互以及更新每个代理的属性。" class="wp-image-1047756" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_skillview.png 3238w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_skillview-300x171.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_skillview-1024x585.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_skillview-768x439.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_skillview-1536x878.png 1536w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_skillview-2048x1170.png 2048w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/New_skillview-240x137.png 240w" sizes="(max-width: 3238px) 100vw, 3238px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> AutoGen 的新可视化画布界面允许用户在同一视图窗格中可视化代理交互并更新每个代理的属性。</figcaption></figure><p><strong>可配置的代理、模型和技能：</strong>通过画布上简单、直接的交互来自定义每个代理的角色和技能。无论您是添加新功能还是调整现有功能，该过程都是简单且用户友好的。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7.png" alt="AutoGen Studio 用户界面：动态原型设计和测试" class="wp-image-1045818" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7.png 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7-300x169.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7-768x432.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7-1066x600.png 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7-655x368.png 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7-240x135.png 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7-640x360.png 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7-960x540.png 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_debug_fig7-1280x720.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">拟议的 AutoGen 视觉画布界面将探索代理内部独白的更新可视化，以改进调试。</figcaption></figure><p><strong>动态原型设计和测试：</strong>实验是完善代理工作流程的关键。通过我们的新界面，您可以对各种代理配置进行原型设计并立即在实时环境中对其进行测试。这种实时交互允许您与工作流程聊天、观察所有代理消息并即时找出需要改进的领域。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8.png" alt="AutoGen Studio 社区画廊" class="wp-image-1045824" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8.png 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8-300x169.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8-768x432.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8-1066x600.png 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8-655x368.png 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8-240x135.png 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8-640x360.png 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8-960x540.png 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/AutoGenStudio_gallery-new_fig8-1280x720.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">新提出的设计探索了一系列可重复使用的精选工作流程和实体（例如技能和代理）。</figcaption></figure><p>最后，我们正在 AutoGen Studio 中开发一个<strong>社区画廊</strong>，用户可以在其中共享、发现和互相学习。该画廊将允许您发布您的工作流程、代理和技能，从而营造一个协作环境，让每个人都可以从共享知识和创新中受益。 </p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="note-on-responsible-ai-promoting-safe-and-ethical-multi-agent-solutions">关于负责任的人工智能的说明：促进安全和道德的多代理解决方案</h2><p>AutoGen Studio 旨在提供一个低代码环境，用于快速原型设计和测试多代理工作流程。我们的目标是负责任地推进解决多个智能体问题的研究和实践，并开发有助于人类福祉的工具。 AutoGen Studio 与 AutoGen 一起致力于实施可促进安全可靠结果的功能。例如，AutoGen Studio 提供分析工具来了解代理操作和防护措施，例如支持用于代码执行的 Docker 环境。此功能有助于确保代理在受控且安全的环境中运行，从而降低意外或有害操作的风险。有关我们在 AutoGen 中实现负责任的 AI 的方法的更多信息，请参阅此处的透明度常见问题解答： <a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://github.com/microsoft/autogen/blob/main/TRANSPARENCY_FAQS.md" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">https://github.com/microsoft/autogen/blob/main/TRANSPARENCY_FAQS.md <span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开）</span></a> 。最后，AutoGen Studio 尚未做好生产准备，即它不专注于实施生产准备部署所需的身份验证和其他安全措施。</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="acknowledgements">致谢</h2><p>我们要感谢开源软件 (OSS) 社区和 Microsoft <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/lab/ai-frontiers/">AI Frontiers</a>组织的成员在此过程中的讨论和反馈。具体来说，我们要感谢<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/pialic/">Piali Choudhury</a> 、 <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/hassanam/">Ahmed Awadallah</a> 、Robin Moeur、 <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/jagerrit/">Jack Gerrits</a> 、Robert Barber、Grace Proebsting、 <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/mpahud/">Michel Pahud</a>和其他人提供的反馈和评论。</p><div style="height:30px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><span id="label-external-link" class="sr-only" aria-hidden="true">在新选项卡中打开</span><p><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/introducing-autogen-studio-a-low-code-interface-for-building-multi-agent-workflows/">AutoGen Studio 简介：用于构建多代理工作流程的低代码界面一</a>文首先出现在<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research">Microsoft Research</a>上。</p> ;
研究重点：2024 年 6 月 10 日当周https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/research-focus-week-of-june-10-2024/Alyssa Hughes Wed, 12 Jun 2024 16:00:00 +0000Research Blog https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/?p=1045134 <p>本期：RELEVANCE 自动评估创意 LLM 回复；可回收的基于 vitrimer 的印刷电路板； Lean Attention：硬件感知的可扩展注意力机制； WaveCoder：微调代码LLM；新的 AutoGen 培训课程。</p><p> 《<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/research-focus-week-of-june-10-2024/">研究焦点：2024 年 6 月 10 日一周》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research">Microsoft Research</a>上。</p> ; 
<figure class="wp-block-pullquote"><blockquote><p><em class="">欢迎来到研究焦点，这是一系列博客文章，重点介绍 Microsoft 研究社区的著名出版物、事件、代码/数据集、新员工和其他里程碑。</em> </p></blockquote></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1400" height="788" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1.png" alt="研究重点：2024 年 6 月 10 日" class="wp-image-1045137" srcset="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1.png 1400w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-300x169.png 300w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-768x432.png 768w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-1066x600.png 1066w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-655x368.png 655w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-240x135.png 240w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-640x360.png 640w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-960x540.png 960w, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/06/RF43-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1-1280x720.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></figure><h3 class="wp-block-heading h6 has-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-c69bca9968646e46b374b38537502a80" id="new-research">新研究</h3><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="relevance-automatic-evaluation-framework-for-llm-responses"> 相关性：LLM 回复的自动评估框架</h2><p>人工智能中的相关性是指信息或操作对特定任务或查询的有用性。它有助于确定搜索引擎、聊天机器人和其他人工智能系统内容的准确性、有效性、效率和用户满意度。</p><p> <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/project/relevance-automatic-evaluation-framework-for-llm-responses/overview/">RELEVANCE</a> （具有纵向反演指标的相关性和基于熵的评估）是由 Microsoft 研究人员设计的生成式 AI 评估框架，用于自动评估大型语言模型 (LLM) 的创造性响应。相关性将定制的相关性评估与数学指标相结合，以确保人工智能生成的内容符合人类标准并保持一致性。随着时间的推移监控这些指标可以自动检测法学硕士的相关性评估何时开始出现偏差或出现幻觉。</p><p>仅定制相关性评估就涉及根据预定义标准对响应进行评分。然而，虽然这些分数提供了直接评估，但它们可能无法捕获多次评估或不同数据集（例如模型幻觉和模型滑移）的反应模式的全部复杂性和动态。为了解决这个问题，RELEVANCE 将数学技术与自定义评估相结合，以确保 LLM 随时间的响应准确性以及对不断发展的 LLM 行为的适应性，而无需手动审核。 </p><div class="wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-1 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex"><div class="wp-block-button is-style-outline"> <a data-bi-type="button" class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/project/relevance-automatic-evaluation-framework-for-llm-responses/overview/">了解更多</a></div></div><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-dots"/><h3 class="wp-block-heading h6 has-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-21d8108ee594aad478409a8aa618b2ee" id="new-research-1">新研究</h3><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="recyclable-vitrimer-based-printed-circuit-boards-for-sustainable-electronics">用于可持续电子产品的可回收基于 vitrimer 的印刷电路板</h2><p>印刷电路板 (PCB) 在电子产品中无处不在，当设备达到使用寿命时，印刷电路板 (PCB) 构成了对环境有害的电子废物的很大一部分。由于在制造过程中使用不可逆固化的热固性环氧树脂，它们的回收具有挑战性。微软和华盛顿大学的研究人员<a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://spectrum.ieee.org/electronic-waste-recycling-2668106144" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">旨在应对这一挑战</a>，并有可能为电子行业的可持续转型铺平道路。在最近发表在《Nature Sustainability： <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/publication/recyclable-vitrimer-based-printed-circuit-boards-for-sustainable-electronics/">用于可持续电子产品的可回收基于 vitrimer 的印刷电路板》</a>的一篇论文中，他们提出了一种使用酯交换 vitrimer (vPCB) 的 PCB 配方以及与标准制造生态系统兼容的端到端制造工艺。这项从摇篮到摇篮的生命周期评估显示，与传统 PCB 相比，vPCB 在 11 个类别中显着减少了环境影响。该团队成功制造了在 vPCB 上传输 2.4 GHz 无线电信号的物联网设备的功能原型，其电气和机械性能符合行业标准。 vPCB 中的断裂和孔洞是可修复的，同时在多个修复周期中保持相当的性能。研究人员还展示了一种基于聚合物用小分子溶剂溶胀的非破坏性回收过程。与传统的溶剂分解回收不同，这种溶胀过程不会降解材料。动态机械分析发现催化剂损失可以忽略不计，储能模量变化最小，并且多个回收周期中的聚合物主链组成相同。这种回收工艺实现了 98% 的聚合物回收率、100% 的纤维回收率和 91% 的溶剂回收率，以制造新的 vPCB，而不会降低性能，从而可能为电子产品的循环利用铺平道路。 </p><div class="wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-2 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex"><div class="wp-block-button is-style-outline"> <a data-bi-type="button" class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/publication/recyclable-vitrimer-based-printed-circuit-boards-for-sustainable-electronics/">阅读论文</a></div></div><div class="border-bottom border-top border-gray-300 mt-5 mb-5 msr-promo text-center text-md-left alignwide" data-bi-aN="promo" data-bi-id="1044945"><p class="msr-promo__label text-gray-800 text-center text-uppercase"><span class="px-4 bg-white display-inline-block font-weight-semibold small">微软研究博客</span></p><div class="row pt-3 pb-4 align-items-center"><div class="msr-promo__media col-12 col-md-5"> <a class="bg-gray-300" href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/introducing-aurora-the-first-large-scale-foundation-model-of-the-atmosphere/" aria-label="Introducing Aurora: The first large-scale foundation model of the atmosphere" data-bi-cN="Introducing Aurora: The first large-scale foundation model of the atmosphere" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" class="w-100 display-block" src="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/uploads/prodnew/2024/05/NEW_Aurora-2024-BlogHeroFeature-1400x788-1.jpg" alt="风暴塞兰的卫星图像" /></a></div><div class="msr-promo__content p-3 px-5 col-12 col-md"><h2 class="h4">介绍极光：第一个大型大气基础模型</h2><p class="large">Aurora 是微软研究院的一个新的人工智能基础模型，它可以通过比以往更快、更准确的天气预报来改变我们预测和减轻极端天气事件以及气候变化影响的能力。 </p><div class="wp-block-buttons justify-content-center justify-content-md-start"><div class="wp-block-button"> <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/introducing-aurora-the-first-large-scale-foundation-model-of-the-atmosphere/" class="btn btn-brand glyph-append glyph-append-chevron-right" aria-label="Learn more" data-bi-cN="Introducing Aurora: The first large-scale foundation model of the atmosphere" target="_blank">了解更多</a></div></div></div><!--/.msr-promo__content--></div><!--/.msr-promo__inner-wrap--><span id="label-external-link" class="sr-only" aria-hidden="true">在新选项卡中打开</span></div><!--/.msr-promo--><h3 class="wp-block-heading h6 has-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-73123c9697b9c6db2728fb2f179fa924" id="new-research-2">新研究</h3><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="leanattention-hardware-aware-scalable-attention-mechanism-for-the-decode-phase-of-transformers"> LeanAttention：变压器解码阶段的硬件感知可扩展注意力机制</h2><p>基于 Transformer 的模型已成为自然语言处理、自然语言生成和图像生成中使用最广泛的架构之一。最先进模型的大小已达到数十亿个参数，需要大量内存并导致显着的推理延迟，即使在图形处理单元 (GPU) 等尖端人工智能加速器上也是如此。尝试满足依赖如此大模型的应用程序的低延迟需求，并不能满足推理过程中不同阶段的计算不同性质，因此无法有效地利用底层硬件。</p><p>在最近的一篇论文： <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/publication/lean-attention-hardware-aware-scalable-attention-mechanism-for-the-decode-phase-of-transformers/">Lean Attention: Hardware-Aware Scalable Attention Mechanism for the Decode-Phase of Transformers</a>中，微软的研究人员提出了一种可扩展的技术，用于计算仅解码器 Transformer 的令牌生成阶段（解码阶段）的自注意力楷模。 LeanAttention 通过重新设计解码阶段的执行流程，能够针对长上下文长度的挑战性情况扩展注意力机制的实现。研究人员表明，在线 softmax 的关联属性可以被视为缩减操作，从而允许他们在这些大上下文长度上并行化注意力计算。他们将平铺计算的“stream-K”式简化扩展为自注意力，以实现并行计算，从而实现接近 100% 的 GPU 利用率，注意力执行速度比 FlashAttention-2 平均提高 2.6 倍，最高可达 8.33 倍512k 上下文长度。 </p><div class="wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-3 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex"><div class="wp-block-button is-style-outline"> <a data-bi-type="button" class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/publication/lean-attention-hardware-aware-scalable-attention-mechanism-for-the-decode-phase-of-transformers/">阅读论文</a></div></div><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-dots"/><h3 class="wp-block-heading h6 has-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-0663ba4d11b1a8df4b8ebb08832c118e" id="new-research-3">新研究</h3><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="wavecoder-widespread-and-versatile-enhanced-instruction-tuning-with-refined-data-generation"> WaveCoder：广泛且多功能的增强型指令调整和精细数据生成</h2><p>最近的研究表明，在高质量指令数据集上进行微调的法学硕士可以获得处理代码相关任务的令人印象深刻的能力。然而，现有的指令数据生成方法经常产生重复数据，并且数据质量可控性不够。</p><p>在最近的一篇论文： <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/publication/wavecoder-widespread-and-versatile-enhanced-instruction-tuning-with-refined-data-generation/">WaveCoder：通过精炼数据生成进行广泛且通用的增强指令调优中</a>，微软的研究人员通过将指令数据分类为四个与代码相关的任务来扩展指令调优的泛化，并提出了一种基于 LLM 的生成器-判别器数据处理框架从开源代码生成多样化、高质量的指令数据。他们推出了 CodeSeaXDataset，这是一个包含 19,915 个指令实例的数据集，涵盖四个通用代码相关任务。此外，他们还推出了 WaveCoder，这是一种经过微调的代码法学硕士，具有广泛且通用的增强指令调整功能。该模型专为增强代码 LLM 的指令调整而设计。他们的实验表明，在相同微调规模水平下，WaveCoder 模型在跨不同代码相关任务的泛化能力方面优于其他开源模型。此外，WaveCoder 在之前的代码生成任务中表现出很高的效率。 </p><div class="wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-4 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex"><div class="wp-block-button is-style-outline"> <a data-bi-type="button" class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/publication/wavecoder-widespread-and-versatile-enhanced-instruction-tuning-with-refined-data-generation/">阅读论文</a></div><div class="wp-block-button is-style-fill-github"><a data-bi-type="button" class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://github.com/microsoft/WaveCoder">获取代码</a></div></div><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-dots"/><h3 class="wp-block-heading h6 has-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-217534cc59c11ea2e7cf0f95df318c71" id="training-course">训练课程</h3><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="new-course-offers-autogen-training">新课程提供 AutoGen 培训</h2><p><a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://www.deeplearning.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">DeepLearning.AI <span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开）</span></a>与 Microsoft 和宾夕法尼亚州立大学合作，提供短期培训课程： <a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://learn.deeplearning.ai/login?callbackUrl=https%3A%2F%2Flearn.deeplearning.ai%2Fcourses%2Fai-agentic-design-patterns-with-autogen%3Futm_campaign%3Dautogen-launch%26utm_medium%3Demail%26_hsenc%3Dp2ANqtz-_bwUbDaYxNzvpaby9JT2sVmJfn9ytor-7fzrHUL79c1E9eeR6-gF8K4SGZ5N4DBEvTwVau-Q8Aue1M-IaPqnGjHKJE2A%26_hsmi%3D309237202%26utm_content%3D309237202%26utm_source%3Dhs_email" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>使用 AutoGen 的 AI 代理设计模式</strong><span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开）</span></a> ，以下一代多代理框架为中心人工智能应用。该课程由 AutoGen 创始人、微软人工智能前沿研究院首席研究员 Chi Wang 和宾夕法尼亚州立大学助理教授吴庆云教授，探讨如何使用 AutoGen 构建和定制多智能体系统，使智能体能够承担不同的角色并进行协作来完成复杂的任务。您可以<a class="msr-external-link glyph-append glyph-append-open-in-new-tab glyph-append-xsmall" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TBNTH-fwGPE" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">在此视频中了解更多详细信息<span class="sr-only">（在新选项卡中打开）</span></a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/autogen-enabling-next-generation-large-language-model-applications/">AutoGen</a>旨在简化 LLM 工作流程的编排、优化和自动化，并作为代理 AI 的通用编程框架被广泛采用。它提供可定制和可对话的代理，利用最先进的 LLM（如 GPT-4）的最强功能，同时通过与人员和工具集成以及通过自动聊天在多个代理之间进行对话来解决其局限性。 </p><div class="wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-5 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex"><div class="wp-block-button is-style-outline"> <a data-bi-type="button" class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://learn.deeplearning.ai/login?callbackUrl=https%3A%2F%2Flearn.deeplearning.ai%2Fcourses%2Fai-agentic-design-patterns-with-autogen%3Futm_campaign%3Dautogen-launch%26utm_medium%3Demail%26_hsenc%3Dp2ANqtz-_bwUbDaYxNzvpaby9JT2sVmJfn9ytor-7fzrHUL79c1E9eeR6-gF8K4SGZ5N4DBEvTwVau-Q8Aue1M-IaPqnGjHKJE2A%26_hsmi%3D309237202%26utm_content%3D309237202%26utm_source%3Dhs_email" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">训练课程</a></div></div><div style="padding-bottom:64px; padding-top:64px" class="wp-block-msr-immersive-section alignfull row has-background has-lighter-gray-background-color has-text-color has-black-color wp-block-msr-immersive-section"><div class="container"><div class="wp-block-msr-immersive-section__inner"><div class="wp-block-msr-cards msr-cards msr-cards--default mt-4 has-text-align-left" data-bi-aN="microsoft-research-in-the-news"><div class="msr-cards__inner"><div class="heading-wrapper"><h2 class="mb-5 ">微软研究院新闻报道</h2></div><div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-lg-3"><div class="msr-cards__card msr-cards__card--default col"><div class="card has-spectrum-border-top__hover material-card h-100 p-0" data-mount="click-group"><div class="card-body bg-white p-4 pt-3"><h3 class="h5"> <a class="text-decoration-none text-black" data-bi-cN="Superfast Microsoft AI is first to predict air pollution for the whole world" href="https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-024-01677-2"><span>超快的微软人工智能首次预测全球空气污染</span><span class="glyph-prepend glyph-prepend-small glyph-prepend-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></h3><p>自然 | 2004 年 6 月 4 日</p><p>微软开发的人工智能模型可以准确预测全世界的天气和空气污染，而且只需不到一分钟。该模型名为“极光”，还可以预测十天的全球天气。 </p></div></div></div><div class="msr-cards__card msr-cards__card--default col"><div class="card has-spectrum-border-top__hover material-card h-100 p-0" data-mount="click-group"><div class="card-body bg-white p-4 pt-3"><h3 class="h5"> <a class="text-decoration-none text-black" data-bi-cN="Chatbot teamwork makes the AI dream work" href="https://link.wired.com/public/35624948"><span>聊天机器人团队合作让人工智能梦想成真</span><span class="glyph-prepend glyph-prepend-small glyph-prepend-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></h3><p>有线| 2024 年 6 月 6 日</p><p>法学硕士经常会被数学问题绊倒，因为他们的工作方式是提供统计上合理的文本，而不是严格的逻辑推理。微软的研究人员表明，让人工智能代理协作可以缓解这一弱点。 </p></div></div></div><div class="msr-cards__card msr-cards__card--default col"><div class="card has-spectrum-border-top__hover material-card h-100 p-0" data-mount="click-group"><div class="card-body bg-white p-4 pt-3"><h3 class="h5"> <a class="text-decoration-none text-black" data-bi-cN="1-bit LLMs Could Solve AI’s Energy Demands - IEEE Spectrum" href="https://spectrum.ieee.org/1-bit-llm"><span>1 位法学硕士可以解决人工智能的能源需求 – IEEE Spectrum</span> <span class="glyph-prepend glyph-prepend-small glyph-prepend-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></h3><p> IEEE 频谱 |2024 年 5 月 30 日</p><p>“一位 LLM 为设计专门针对 1 位 LLM 优化的定制硬件和系统打开了新的大门，”- Furu Wei，微软研究院。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="justify-content-center text-center mb-4"> <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/news-and-awards/" class="btn btn-outline-primary glyph-append glyph-append-small glyph-append-chevron-right msr-cards__cta" data-bi-cN="View more news and awards" data-bi-type="button">查看更多新闻和奖项</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><span id="label-external-link" class="sr-only" aria-hidden="true">在新选项卡中打开</span><p>《<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/research-focus-week-of-june-10-2024/">研究焦点：2024 年 6 月 10 日一周》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research">Microsoft Research</a>上。</p> ;
